<taxonomicName id="2697BC2EE38B557F1B01210F717E0380" authority="Br." authorityName="Br." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Artemisia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="588" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="nivalis">
Artemisia 
<normalizedToken id="C52C18B83E95D5FEFB2331D0F7C217FF" originalValue="nivális" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">nivalis</normalizedToken>
Br.
</taxonomicName>
-Bl.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="597D633311B33AABD73B0DA412A508C2" pageId="null" pageNumber="588" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="9F35CDC85CF65284F16185E86F0B492D" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">Schnee-Edelraute</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="373875596CC7D77FABE8E74909DEB9B7" pageId="null" pageNumber="588" type="description">
<paragraph id="CE286E55B84746200D9A1B718C1EA0D9" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="C3F5207923AA1DB3F9E6B68C30158234" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Artemisia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="588" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="genipi">
<emphasis id="DC1E70D6EF489C473552C41F0A1EA82B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">A. Genipi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 14f) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="099C03C239577DEE4DC154F1C081AC8F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">Pflanze kahl</emphasis>
(alle andern Arten der Artengruppe graufilzig behaart); 
<emphasis id="1C8BB29EFD8602EC2543860BD7558D2D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">
<normalizedToken id="F3102B85EB0484C32D95F711B66DE14B" originalValue="Köpfe" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">Koepfe</normalizedToken>
im Durchmesser 2
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="D217934A3E962E60597E6C7678C09573" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">
3 mm; 
<normalizedToken id="B5DDEC740BC8FFBB68AAA84E65CF2B0A" originalValue="Früchte" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">Fruechte</normalizedToken>
kahl
</emphasis>
. - 
<normalizedToken id="BD6AF804056C21C279BF5AB9AEF3D995" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4F663F3DE2DDB360BDBC6935ABB017BF" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">
<emphasis id="39F2F7BBF4C7A4E8BEEEB250594F0260" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">Zytologische Angaben</emphasis>
. Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="DA7B7D8E5970EB4DECFCE17D5376D02B" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">
<emphasis id="4D94312E85AD50D506DFDD13D48B00D0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">Standort</emphasis>
. Alpin (bis 
<normalizedToken id="C26BA17385106D438AC8D6AF8DF23E96" originalValue="über" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">ueber</normalizedToken>
3400 m). Felsen, Felsschutt.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="50560BE868FCDBA78B3F0C8B5197F9D5" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">
<emphasis id="18876828DBA2983D280ED87197499DD0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">Verbreitung. Penninische Pflanze:</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="10FC651BB1138D1A70B3BF6FE1CCDECD" originalValue="Südliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">Suedliche</normalizedToken>
Walliser Alpen (Seillon im Val des Dix, Oberrothorn bei Zermatt).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="911AF93F9DF6B88FA56ED36FE8B50976" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">
<emphasis id="9B9E695BF088047EA333DE4635726BD3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">Bemerkungen</emphasis>
. Nach Heske (1969) handelt es sich bei 
<taxonomicName id="ECD2F33545EADA04C6057BF59311E87C" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Artemisia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="588" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="nivalis">
<emphasis id="07269C45BAF8B93DB48F8026499F84C3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">A. nivalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
nur um eine kahle Form von 
<taxonomicName id="D3A1FE66051FA10156F5C11D9F434AF8" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Artemisia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="588" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="genipi">
<emphasis id="EECD4F0634EADEDDB234A8A282612A0C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">A. Genipi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 14f) und nicht um eine 
<normalizedToken id="660F4764A149F3AD809AB9AE916F9431" originalValue="selbständige" pageId="null" pageNumber="588">selbstaendige</normalizedToken>
Art.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
